The Quran translation texts included in the data/ directory are the
intellectual property of their respective publishers, primarily the
King Fahd Complex for the Printing of the Holy Quran, Madinah,
Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. These texts are reproduced here for
non-commercial, educational, and technical purposes only.

This is an UNOFFICIAL, INDEPENDENT project with no affiliation to or
endorsement from the King Fahd Complex. Texts were extracted via
automated OCR and AI-assisted tools and may contain errors.

The repository maintainers:
- Make no claim of ownership over any translation text
- Make no guarantee of accuracy — OCR and digitization errors may exist
- Bear no responsibility for any errors, omissions, modification, or
  misuse of the texts by third parties
- Strongly advise all users to verify any text against the official
  printed editions issued by the King Fahd Complex before use in
  any religious, educational, or production context

Users who discover any discrepancy are encouraged to report it via
GitHub Issues with a reference to the official printed source.
